{"lemma":"أَسْرَع","slug":"أَسْرَع","root":"س.ر.ع","root_slug":"س-ر-ع","root_link":"/words/roots/س-ر-ع","pos":"N","pos_camel":"noun","paradigm":[],"frequency_in_corpus":0,"cross_references":{"qac":{"found":true,"lemma_key":"أَسْرَع","root":"سرع","pos":"N","occurrence_count":2},"wiktextract":{"found":true,"entry_count":1,"pos_tags":["verb"],"has_etymology":false,"sense_count":0},"lanes":{"found":true,"entry_ids":["n19584","n19594"],"search_url":"https://lanelexicon.com/?s=%D8%A3%D9%8E%D8%B3%D9%92%D8%B1%D9%8E%D8%B9"}},"translations":null,"definition":null,"etymology":null,"ipa":null,"lanes_definition":{"source":"lanes","entries":[{"entry_id":"n19584","headword_ar":"اسرع","root":"srE","body":[{"kind":"text","text":"is originally trans.; (S, K;) [signifying"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"He quickened,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"hastened,"},{"kind":"text","text":"himself, or his going, &c.;] and hence the saying, in a trad.,"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"A_i*aA mar~a","text_ar":"اـِذَا مَرَّ"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"A^aHadukumo biTirobaAlK maAy^ilK faloyusoriEi Alma$oYa","text_ar":"اَحَدُكُمْ بِطِرْبَالٍ مَايِلٍ فَلْيُسْرِعِ المَشْىَ"},{"kind":"text","text":"["},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"When any one of you passes by a high wall,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"the like,"},{"kind":"text","text":"that is"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"inclining, let him quicken,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"hasten, the pace,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"going"},{"kind":"text","text":"]. (K, * TA.) But [it is used also elliptically, as meaning"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"He hastened, in an intrans. sense; he made haste; he sped; he went quickly;"},{"kind":"text","text":"and hence] you say,"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"AsrE fiY Als~ayori","text_ar":"اسرع فِى السَّيْرِ"},{"kind":"text","text":", (S, K,) like"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"saruEa","text_ar":"سَرُعَ"},{"kind":"text","text":"["},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"He was quick, expeditious, hasty, speedy, rapid, swift,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"fleet, in going, journeying,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"pace"},{"kind":"text","text":"]: (K:) or [rather"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"he hastened, made haste,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"sped, therein;"},{"kind":"text","text":"for]"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"AsrE","text_ar":"اسرع"},{"kind":"text","text":"signifies"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"he endeavoured,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"sought,"},{"kind":"text","text":"and"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"affected, to be quick,"},{"kind":"text","text":"&c.,"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"as though he hastened the pace,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"going;"},{"kind":"text","text":"but ↓"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"saruEa","text_ar":"سَرُعَ","orth_type":"arrow"},{"kind":"text","text":"denotes what is as it were an innate quality: (Sb:) the verb being originally trans., when you say of one"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"AsrE fY Alsyr","text_ar":"اسرع فى السير"},{"kind":"text","text":"it is as though [meaning]"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"he urged himself forward with haste;"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"he quickened,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"hastened, the pace,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"going;"},{"kind":"text","text":"and it is only because the meaning is understood by the persons addressing one another, that the objective complement is not expressed: (Lth, K:) or the verb may be trans. by means of a particle and without a particle: or when made immediately trans., the phrase may be meant to be understood as elliptical. (TA.) [Accord. to Fei,]"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"AsrE fiY","text_ar":"اسرع فِى"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"ma$oyihi","text_ar":"مَشْيِهِ"},{"kind":"text","text":", &c., inf. n."},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"A_isoraAEN","text_ar":"اـِسْرَاعٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":", is originally"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"AsrE ma$oyahu","text_ar":"اسرع مَشْيَهُ"},{"kind":"text","text":"["},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"He quickened,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"hastened, his pace,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"going"},{"kind":"text","text":"];"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"fY","text_ar":"فى"},{"kind":"text","text":"being redundant; or"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"AsrE AlHarakapa fiY ma$oyihi","text_ar":"اسرع الحَرَكَةَ فِى مَشْيِهِ"},{"kind":"text","text":"["},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"he quickened,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"hastened, the motion in his going"},{"kind":"text","text":"]: and"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"AsrE A_ilayohi","text_ar":"اسرع اـِلَيْهِ"},{"kind":"text","text":"means"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"AsrE AlmuDiY~a A_ilayohi","text_ar":"اسرع المُضِىَّ اـِلَيْهِ"},{"kind":"text","text":"["},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"he quickened,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"hastened, the going to him"},{"kind":"text","text":"]. (Msb.) ↓"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"sr~E","text_ar":"سرّع","orth_type":"arrow"},{"kind":"text","text":"is syn. with"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"AsrE","text_ar":"اسرع"},{"kind":"text","text":". (TA.) And you say,"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"A_ilaY Al$~ar~i","text_ar":"اـِلَى الشَّرِّ"},{"kind":"text","text":"↓"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"tsr~E","text_ar":"تسرّع","orth_type":"arrow"},{"kind":"text","text":", (S, K,) meaning"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"He hastened,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"made haste, to"},{"kind":"text","text":"[do]"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"evil,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"mischief;"},{"kind":"text","text":"(K;) as also"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"tzr~E","text_ar":"تزرّع"},{"kind":"text","text":". (Sgh and K in art."},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"zrE","text_ar":"زرع"},{"kind":"text","text":".) And ↓"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"tsr~E","text_ar":"تسرّع","orth_type":"arrow"},{"kind":"page_break","n":1350},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"biAlA^amori","text_ar":"بِالاَمْرِ"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"He hastened to do the thing,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"affair;"},{"kind":"text","text":"syn."},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"baAdara bihi","text_ar":"بَادَرَ بِهِ"},{"kind":"text","text":". (TA.) See also 3. ―         -b2-"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"AsrE A_ilayohi","text_ar":"اسرع اـِلَيْهِ"},{"kind":"text","text":"occurs in a trad. as meaning"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"He was quick,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"hasty, in being angry with him,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"in blaming him,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"in reviling him."},{"kind":"text","text":"(Mgh.) ―         -b3-"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"AsrE bihi","text_ar":"اسرع بِهِ"},{"kind":"text","text":": see [its contr.]"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"baT~aA^a bihi","text_ar":"بَطَّاَ بِهِ"},{"kind":"text","text":". ―         -b4-"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"A^asoraEuwA","text_ar":"اَسْرَعُوا"},{"kind":"text","text":"signifies also,"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"Their beasts on which they rode were,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"became, quick, swift,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"fleet."},{"kind":"text","text":"(AZ, S, K.)       -A2-"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"maA A^asoraEa maA SanaEota","text_ar":"مَا اَسْرَعَ مَا صَنَعْتَ"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"ka*aA","text_ar":"كَذَا"},{"kind":"text","text":"["},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"How quick was thy doing that!"},{"kind":"text","text":"]. (S, K.)"}],"source_refs":["S","K","Sb","Lth"]},{"entry_id":"n19594","headword_ar":"اَسْرَعُ","root":"srE","body":[{"kind":"text","text":"["},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"More,"},{"kind":"text","text":"and"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"most, quick, expeditious, hasty, speedy, rapid, swift,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"fleet,"},{"kind":"text","text":"of course, tendency, action, speech, &c.]. [It is said, of God, in the Kur vi. 62,]"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"wahuwa A^asoraEu AlHaAsibiyna","text_ar":"وَهُوَ اَسْرَعُ الحَاسِبِينَ"},{"kind":"text","text":"["},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"And He is the quickest of the reckoners"},{"kind":"text","text":"]. (K.) [The fem.]"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"suroEaY","text_ar":"سُرْعَى"},{"kind":"text","text":"is applied to a she-camel by Honeyf El-Hanátim [as meaning"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"Surpassingly quick"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"fleet"},{"kind":"text","text":"]. (IAar, TA in art."},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"bhY","text_ar":"بهى"},{"kind":"text","text":".)"}],"source_refs":[]}]},"classical_definitions":null}